Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:13.70,Default,EC Boy,0,0,0,,{I forget the name, \Nbut the girl from Class 2—}Quên tên rồi nhưng hình như bên lớp 2--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:15.80,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The name's Gotoh.}Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.66,Default,Mob 1,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-sama!}Ngài Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.70,Default,Mob 2,0,0,0,,{Hold me!}Ôm em đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.54,Default,Mob 3,0,0,0,,{You're a living national treasure!}Ngài là báu vật sống!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:29.56,Default,Mob 4,0,0,0,,Gotoh! Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.51,Default,Mob 4,0,0,0,,Gotoh! Gotoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.11,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,{...six votes for a haunted house,}... 6 phiếu nhà ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.86,Default,Classmate C,0,0,0,,{and two votes for a candy shop.}và 2 phiếu cửa hàng kẹo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{How long have I been out?}Mình ngủ bao lâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:45.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I think I was in homeroom, and they started \Ntalking about festival project ideas...}Hình như đang bàn xem lễ hội văn hoá làm gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:46.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's no use.}Không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:49.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Everything after the word \N"unity" came up is a blank.}Mọi thứ từ sau chữ "đoàn kết" đều mơ hồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.84,DefaultTop,Classmate C,0,0,0,,Vậy thì theo đa số phiếu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.23,DefaultTop,Classmate C,0,0,0,,{Class 2's project will be \Na maid and butler cafe!}Lớp 2 sẽ làm quán cà phê hầu gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.89,Default,Classmate X,0,0,0,,{We'll have to get lots of maid uniforms!}Vậy thì phải tìm nhiều đồ hầu gái thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:56.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{M-Maid?}H-Hầu gái?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.88,Default,Classmate Y,0,0,0,,{Since all the girls'll be wearing them!}Vì tất cả bạn nữ đều mặc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.20,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{All the girls?!}T-Tất cả bạn nữ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Does that include... me?}Là cả... mình á?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:03.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-No way!}K-Không thể nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Too far outside my skill set!}Quá cao cấp so với mình!
