Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A band performance application...}Đơn nguyện vọng biểu diễn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Kessoku Band...}Ban nhạc Kessoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Who wrote all this?!}Ai viết?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What? Hitori Gotoh wrote it?!}Hả? Gotoh Hitori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm a professional guitarist now!}Giờ mình là tay ghita chuyên nghiệp rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Begone, lust for culture festival attention!}Biến đi, khao khát biểu diễn ở lễ hội văn hoá!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Focus on your band's career!}Tập trung vào sự nghiệp ban nhạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:21.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Good... the lust is fading.}May quá... ảo tưởng đang biến mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was that?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.00,Default,SC President,0,0,0,,{Teacher! Someone's collapsed out here!}Mau gọi giáo viên! Mau gọi giáo viên!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.44,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.81,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.19,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.94,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.58,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.95,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.59,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.42,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:12.38,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.80,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:22.60,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:26.73,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:32.79,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum in a harmonizing quartet}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.78,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to cause a revolution}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:42.79,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum in a lamenting forte}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:47.54,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild}
