Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.91,0:07:26.84,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\an8\c&H282A31&\pos(523.5,30.5)}{Disciplinary Notice\N}{\fs16}{Class 1-2\N}{\fs20}{Hitori Gotoh \N\N}{\fs12}{Reason for Reprimand\N}{\fs8}{For singing a song with extremely depressing lyrics\Nat a culture festival intended to hype people up,\Nthe aforementioned is officially expelled\Nunder article 50 of the school code.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.11,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{something other than seishun rock \Nat a high school culture festival?}vì đã tận hưởng tuổi thanh xuân nhạc rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Làm gì có chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.30,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I get why Bocchi's scared, though.}Chị hiểu tại sao em do dự.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.99,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{There's a chance—a likelihood, rather—that \Nyou'll be playing in front of a large crowd.}Nếu chơi tệ sẽ thành trò cười của đám đông.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.49,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{So you don't have to rush to a decision.}Thế nên đừng vội vã quyết định.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.60,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ryo-san...}Chị Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:47.22,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I still have nightmares\Nabout that concert I bombed.}Nói thật chị vẫn còn kí ức kinh khủng lần đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.86,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{So you were just acting strong earlier?}Lúc nãy tỏ ra mạnh mẽ à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:53.69,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Either way, just make sure\Nyou don't have any regrets, Bocchi-chan.}Tóm lại hãy quyết định để sau này không hối hận.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.36,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{Wise words.}Đúng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.87,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{G-Got it.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.62,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll think it over.}Em sẽ nghĩ về nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.45,Default,Nijika/Ryo,0,0,0,,{Right, right!}Ừm ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:06.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Nijika-chan wants to play \Nat the culture festival too.}Nijika muốn tham gia biểu diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:13.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I bet it'd feel pretty darn good...}Cảm xúc lúc đó sẽ tuyệt lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I just can't do it!}Không thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, everyone.}Xin lỗi mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I thought I could do it \Nyesterday, but I can't.}Hôm qua em tưởng làm được nhưng không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But Nijika-chan told me to make \Nsure I don't have any regrets,}N-Nhưng Nijika nói là đừng để sau này hối hận.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:38.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and if I blow it, I don't think I could \Nmake it through the rest of high school...}Và nếu thất bại thì sẽ thành trò cười cho cả trường...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm already nervous \Nabout playing in a club.}Diễn ở club đã đủ lo lắng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The thought of being \Non stage at a festival...}Lần này còn trên sân khấu lớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yeah, just not happening.}Ừm, không thể đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16\blur3\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H2260DA&\3c&HADE7DC&\pos(59,64)}{Skyrocketing to fame!\N}{\blur0\c&H54A1ED&\3c&H0F5BAA&\bord1.5}{Let's look into }{\c&HFFF3F1&\3c&HE80003&}{the members of }{\3c&HFFF3F1&\c&HE80003&}{Kessoku Band!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1.5\fs9\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&\pos(619.5,68.5)}{The unexpected past of super-popular guitarist\N }{\3c&H006B60&}{Hitori Gotoh, }{\3c&H6B0B16&}{whose }{\c&HA05C00&\3c&HF5D499&}{cool personality, }{\c&HB81B57&\3c&HFCABE3&}{skillful playing,\N }{\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&}{and }{\c&H5C48BD&\3c&HE0D3F6&}{raw lyrics }{\c&HFFEEF2&\3c&H6B0B16&}{have captured the hearts of fans!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:51.46,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs10\c&H20241F&\pos(77.5,349.5)\3c&HA8ABA9&\bord1.5}{Hitori Gotoh}
